    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been meticulously maintained. The engine is robust and responsive, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, providing a confident driving experience. While the exterior shows some light surface scratches and the interior has minor wear on the driver's seat bolster, the car remains mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a solid, well-cared-for vehicle without the price tag of a brand-new model.",
