      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014totally flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have! It's super clean and ready for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
