    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3 that serves as a benchmark for the chassis. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, where the individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing operate with factory precision. The mechanical integrity is superlative; the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with distinct, tight gates. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing original-spec bushings and dampers to maintain the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. The limited-slip differential is silent and provides immediate lock-up under load. Every fluid has been analyzed, and the valve clearances are within tight tolerances. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and zero deferred maintenance.",
